        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle Public User Takes an Exam\n\nactor \&quot;Public User\&quot; as User\nparticipant System\nparticipant ExamAttempt\nparticipant Question\nparticipant Certificate\nparticipant Notification\nparticipant Inspector\n\nUser -&gt; System : select exam\nSystem -&gt; User : display exam details\n\nUser -&gt; System : start exam\n\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : create attempt (status=in-progress)\nSystem -&gt; User : present first question (with timer)\n\nloop for each question\nUser -&gt; System : submit answer\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : save answer (auto-save)\n\nalt if time expires\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : auto-submit\nend\n\nend\n\nUser -&gt; System : finish exam\n\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : calculate score\n\nalt manual grading needed\nInspector -&gt; System : grade essay questions\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : update score\nend\n\nSystem -&gt; ExamAttempt : determine pass/fail\n\nalt if passed\nSystem -&gt; Certificate : generate certificate\nCertificate -&gt; System : return certificate URL\nSystem -&gt; User : display result with certificate link\n\nelse if failed\nSystem -&gt; User : display fail result with retry info\nend\n\nSystem -&gt; Notification : send result notification\nNotification -&gt; User : notify result\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="u-tCzcbDG6vQhc4Li0sd-3">
